See the [http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/Help:Template Mediawiki Template Help] page for general info about how templates work. News entries work like this (example):

<nowiki>
{{Newsitem|date=9 February 2005 (2005-02-09)|author=[[Sham Chukoury]]|title=News page added!|text=The XMMS2 wiki now has a news page!}}
</nowiki>

Notes about formatting:
* Dates must be '%e %B %Y (%Y-%m-%d)' (see date(1)), i.e. '<date> <month> <year> (<ISO8601-style date>)'
* Author names should preferably link to the wiki user page, i.e. <nowiki>[[Joe Bloggs]]</nowiki>